Zaghro Hotel is an excellent choice for travelers visiting Ouarzazate, offering a family-friendly environment alongside many helpful amenities designed to enhance your stay.

The rooms offer air conditioning and a sofa, and getting online is possible, as free wifi is available, allowing you to rest and refresh with ease.

Zaghro Hotel features a 24 hour front desk, room service, and a concierge. In addition, as a valued Zaghro Hotel guest, you can enjoy a pool and an on-site restaurant that are available on-site. Guests arriving by vehicle have access to free parking.

Kasbah of Tifoultoute (2.8 mi), located nearby, makes Zaghro Hotel a great place to stay for those interested in visiting this popular Ouarzazate landmark.

While staying at Zaghro Hotel, you may want to check out La Rose Des Sables Restaurant Pizzeria (0.2 mi) which is a short walk away.

Plus, during your trip, don't forget to check out an architectural building, such as Taourirt Kasbah.

Enjoy your stay in Ouarzazate!
